annotations

Annotation Type Parameters


  • @Documented
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=CONSTRUCTOR)
public @interface Parameters
    It annotation has to be used by Registrable object. And denota the type of parameters that will be injected to the constructor of Registrable problem.
